{"tid":2175123,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"上ig book左salon整緊預感中硬伏","createTime":"2020-08-26T10:08:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T19:09:35.000Z","uid":245710,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"1f6fab883690e738fcbf1cbe5c59db0ccc250995","tid":2175123,"uid":245710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:08:26.000Z","msg":"上到嚟傾已經感覺佢唔想做<br />\n問佢整babylight就話咩唔係咁整唔好睇㗎咪整啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以最後話漂左先再諗<br />\n問題嚟啦漂頭直接上咩都冇<br />\n頭皮保護唔L需要佢啲客人全部頭鐵做驚乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲到搽到同頭皮零距離親密接觸那到pk<br />\n跟住我同我fd就被人放置play左一個鐘以上<br />\n中途睇左幾次唔洗不單止仲要補!?<br />\n屌你咩老細成個鐘啦補都冇用㗎要洗左再漂㗎嘛識唔識do㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4001d803f9b26725b6f45f5906fea878502073e4","tid":2175123,"uid":337986,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:13:11.000Z","msg":"唔開名？"},{"pid":"d8facb9968d24e38f1302f01ec9c790e483238b1","tid":2175123,"uid":245710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:15:25.000Z","msg":"終於可以洗頭<br />\n洗完發現頭髮變橡根<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自已係屋漂都唔會一次個髮質差成咁<br />\n講返先我最後一次自已漂係好耐之前而漂過嘅都已經剪哂<br />\n宜家個頭淨係經歷過染頭髮<br />\n吹完頭變左稻草梳唔到<br />\n雖然我知漂傷頭髮但係呢個太離譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢幫我吹完頭之後我去廁所望左下<br />\n仆街個頭撳落去勁痛<br />\n個頭皮勁多傷口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85d8369d37e9d7efdfa06fdc1858886698c734c","tid":2175123,"uid":245710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4001d803f9b26725b6f45f5906fea878502073e4","tid":2175123,"uid":337986,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:13:11.000Z","msg":"唔開名？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:16:06.000Z","msg":"今晚翻去睇下點先仲未染完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a630ce30d8b2894a108aa98336da3820cf19766c","tid":2175123,"uid":243455,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:17:54.000Z","msg":"建議樓豬爬下文：<br />\n一人一間睇咗IG廣告去幫襯嘅Salon/髮型師 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2116792\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2116792</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n好多ig salon 都好伏<br />\n利申：奶過2次野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開頭問又話乜都整到，去到又話整唔到。整完出黎完全唔係我想要嘅效果，仲要叫我之後keep住搵返佢先維持到，心諗，搵你老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />某一間ig salon嘅死tb"},{"pid":"9a6604ee8dd4076705c955d4dd784cbd1c6290b8","tid":2175123,"uid":245710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:21:39.000Z","msg":"本身打算染淺色系比佢咁搞個頭根本漂唔到第二次 <br />\n只可以再揀第二隻色<br />\n染嘅時侯又嚟啦冇頭皮保護<br />\n染膏同頭零距離接觸<br />\n講錯左係負距離因為仆街啲染膏入左傷口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n那到升天 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n實在忍唔到同佢講頭有傷口好那<br />\n叫我忍下啦話我頭皮敏感???<br />\n你條pk咩春保護都冇好難唔敏感仲要放置play咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff77c9df31e2b9331df4a704a6caad18e01f3f5","tid":2175123,"uid":245710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:25:26.000Z","msg":"就快升天真係頂唔順那到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c24dcc127c687a5aed064c203df1aa9c2decbe","tid":2175123,"uid":245710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a630ce30d8b2894a108aa98336da3820cf19766c","tid":2175123,"uid":243455,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:17:54.000Z","msg":"建議樓豬爬下文：<br />\n一人一間睇咗IG廣告去幫襯嘅Salon/髮型師 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2116792\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2116792</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n好多ig salon 都好伏<br />\n利申：奶過2次野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開頭問又話乜都整到，去到又話整唔到。整完出黎完全唔係我想要嘅效果，仲要叫我之後keep